OL,3,CParents jailed over death of three-
OL,4,Cmonth-old girl
OL,6,FThe parents who caused serious harm to
OL,7,Ftheir three-month-old daughter before
OL,8,Fshe died have been jailed.
OL,10,FJack William Davies, 26, and Terrie
OL,11,FMarie Wood, 23, from Stafford, were
OL,12,Ffound guilty of causing and allowing a
OL,13,Fchild to suffer serious physical harm
OL,14,Fby a jury last October.
OL,16,FDavies was sentenced to two years and
OL,17,FWood for one year and eight months at
OL,18,FBirmingham Crown Court on Tuesday.
