OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772025560
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of three-
OL,4,Cmonth-old girl
OL,6,FStaffordshire Police were called by
OL,7,FWest Midlands Ambulance Service just
OL,8,Fafter 8:30 am on the 5 February 2021
OL,9,Fafter attending a three-month-old girl
OL,10,Fwho had gone into cardiac arrest. She
OL,11,Fdied on the way to hospital.
OL,13,FA postmortem showed there was no
OL,14,Fnatural cause for the death. It also
OL,15,Ffound evidence of a head injury and
OL,16,Fmultiple rib fractures.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
