PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1772025560
OL,3,CParents jailed over death of three-
OL,4,Cmonth-old girl
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Claire Mace, from
OL,7,Fthe child protection team at
OL,8,FStaffordshire Police, said: "This was
OL,9,Fan incredibly distressing case for all
OL,10,Fagencies involved.
OL,12,F"Today's sentencing sends a clear
OL,13,Fmessage that violence against children
OL,14,Fwill never be tolerated. My thoughts
OL,15,Fremain with everyone affected by this
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,F"We will continue to work with our
OL,19,Fpartners to protect children from
OL,20,Fharm, safeguard them and prevent
OL,21,Ftragic cases like this one."
